The '''Elmer Smith Power Plant''' is a [[coal-fired power plant]] owned and operated by the city of [[Owensboro, Kentucky]]. It opened in 1964.
== Emissions data == *2006 CO2 Emissions: 2,846,615 tons *2006 SO2 Emissions: 2,525 tons *2006 NOx Emissions: 7,045 tons *2005 Mercury Emissions: 59 lb
